<cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0056a" xml:id="I01.0021.0056a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0056a00" type="honorific"/><cb:docNumber>No. 21</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0056a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>馬鳴寺根法師碑</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0056a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0056a0101">馬鳴寺</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0056b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0056b0101">魏故
<lb ed="I" n="0056b02" type="honorific"/>根法
<lb ed="I" n="0056b03" type="honorific"/>師之</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0056c01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0056c0101"><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">師</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">諱</unclear>□□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">子</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">孫</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">也</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">法</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">師</unclear>□□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">稟</unclear>。五緯□□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">生</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0056c02" type="honorific"/>□知□□□於齠歲。潔行與白<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">雪</unclear>爭光。溫<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">穆</unclear>與鮮雲<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0056001" n="0056001"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0056001" n="0056001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0056001" n="0056001"/>競<anchor xml:id="end0056001"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">潤</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">爰</unclear>自弱年。英聲早集。
<lb ed="I" n="0056c03" type="honorific"/>孝敬天然。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">曾</unclear>閔無以喻其性。敏悟<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">冠</unclear>時。顏冉<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0056002" n="0056002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0056002" n="0056002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0056002" n="0056002"/>罕<anchor xml:id="end0056002"/>得比其高。堯昂孤上。如長林之
<lb ed="I" n="0056c04" type="honorific"/>出層雲。婉順迎襟。若清泉之入巨<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">壑</unclear>。湛〃然涇渭不能渾其津。灼〃乎<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0056003" n="0056003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0056003" n="0056003"/><anchor xml:id="beg0056003" n="0056003"/>泥<anchor xml:id="end0056003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0056004" n="0056004"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0056004" n="0056004"/><anchor xml:id="beg0056004" n="0056004"/>滓<anchor xml:id="end0056004"/>莫
<lb ed="I" n="0056c05" type="honorific"/>能弊其輝。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">墻</unclear>岸崇峻。可聞而不可見。器韻堅廣。可<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0056005" n="0056005"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0056005" n="0056005"/><anchor xml:id="beg0056005" n="0056005"/>鑽<anchor xml:id="end0056005"/>而不入。故使行逾素。德逾
<lb ed="I" n="0056c06" type="honorific"/>深。志彌著。業彌遠。於是鸞舉<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0056006" n="0056006"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0056006" n="0056006"/><anchor xml:id="beg0056006" n="0056006"/>拔<anchor xml:id="end0056006"/>俗。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">聳</unclear>慮法山之頂。鳳轉去塵。締誠滅影之域。識
<lb ed="I" n="0056c07" type="honorific"/>火搆之弗康。了化城之休止。遂能<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">討</unclear>□三乘。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">機</unclear>御十地。大夏閑居。授講後生。四
<lb ed="I" n="0056c08" type="honorific"/>方慕義。雲會如至。雖鳩公之在<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">灞</unclear>西。未淂方其輻湊。朗上之在汶北。曷以加其
<lb ed="I" n="0056c09" type="honorific"/>歸市。若夫八關之夜。立論之<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">際</unclear>。法師淵<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">瞻</unclear>凌發。風機獨遠。判沖<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">微</unclear>於百氏之中。
<lb ed="I" n="0056c10" type="honorific"/>裁疑滯於一攬之內。理與妙共長。辭與玄同遠。興難則<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">眾</unclear><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0056007" n="0056007"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0056007" n="0056007"/><anchor xml:id="beg0056007" n="0056007"/>席<anchor xml:id="end0056007"/>喪氣。復問則道俗
<lb ed="I" n="0056c11" type="honorific"/>雷解。音清調逸。雅有義宗。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">至</unclear>如課己追真。造次弗<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0056008" n="0056008"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0056008" n="0056008"/><anchor xml:id="beg0056008" n="0056008"/>爽<anchor xml:id="end0056008"/>。禪念求道。終生莫輟。割寶
<lb ed="I" n="0056c12" type="honorific"/>營福。捨物如遺。造經數千。布滿繢素。刊建　聖顏。抽珍裁飾。祇洹妙<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0056009" n="0056009"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0056009" n="0056009"/><anchor xml:id="beg0056009" n="0056009"/>宇<anchor xml:id="end0056009"/>。靡不瓖
<lb ed="I" n="0056c13" type="honorific"/>麗。雖漢明寤寐金人。篾以過茲工也。方當虛器以導迷途。憑福以敷釋典。嘗不
<lb ed="I" n="0056c14" type="honorific"/>憖遺。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">忽</unclear>焉物化。春秋五十五。以正光四年歲次癸卯二月戊午朔三日庚申。殂
<lb ed="I" n="0056c15" type="honorific"/>於寺。攸〃道俗。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">莫</unclear>不悲悼。豈唯痛結師徒而已哉。粵翌日窆於含霞山之陰。法
<lb ed="I" n="0056c16" type="honorific"/>師弟子三百人等。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">並</unclear>聰慧一時。道器斯蔚。追匠誨之无極。痛寒泉之方遠。綴徽
<lb ed="I" n="0056c17" type="honorific"/>音於□□。□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">道</unclear>聲於墳標。其辭曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0056c18" type="honorific"/>昂藏<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">峻</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">緒</unclear>。渺<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">漫</unclear>長<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">灡</unclear>。繽紛組帶。蟬聯纓冠。或智或愚。能危能安。<note place="inline">其一</note>哲人云舉。叶
<lb ed="I" n="0056c19" type="honorific"/>自<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">智</unclear>靈。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">仰</unclear>□旻緯。府藉華涇。淵虯其志。雲鵠其聲。在素玉潤。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0056010" n="0056010"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0056010" n="0056010"/><anchor xml:id="beg0056010" n="0056010"/>處<anchor xml:id="end0056010"/>默金貞。去此火
<lb ed="I" n="0056c20" type="honorific"/>宅。歸彼<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">化</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">城</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">玄</unclear>詞必討。妙理斯征。有有用曉。無無是磬。易和難<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0056011" n="0056011"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0056011" n="0056011"/><anchor xml:id="beg0056011" n="0056011"/>染<anchor xml:id="end0056011"/>。載沖載盈。<note place="inline">其二</note>
<lb ed="I" n="0056c21" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">浩</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">〃</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">精</unclear>□。□□深冰。辟諧法器。自何能稱。識非塵幕。悟是梵乘。飾相莊譯。珍麗
<lb ed="I" n="0056c22" type="honorific"/>□□□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">道</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">徵</unclear>□□□□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">憑</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">刊</unclear>茲茂跡。不朽不凌。</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
